  "detailed_description": "<h1>2-4 Player Local Multiplayer with Keyboard and Xbox Controllers via Steam Remote Play Together</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/29ec6384e085c22c5e8d30ed093e6271.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/52448221eedb8f86e5089d22080ec47a.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer duel of pirates on a single keyboard or via Remote Play Together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/6f47af11f2a0579dd6fedad90f743799.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/6f47af11f2a0579dd6fedad90f743799.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/6f47af11f2a0579dd6fedad90f743799.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from various seas to fight on and customize your match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/0dbeff415742bf8a288e371608581454.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/0dbeff415742bf8a288e371608581454.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/0dbeff415742bf8a288e371608581454.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pirate warfare is easy to pick up, but hard to master. Navigate your ship on the treacherous seas, avoid traps, collect power ups and line up your cannons for a perfects shot in the perfect time to deal devastating damage to your opponent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/2b5612be21f25ad5e96dc9cbd3ebcd5d.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/2b5612be21f25ad5e96dc9cbd3ebcd5d.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/2b5612be21f25ad5e96dc9cbd3ebcd5d.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between different ships with different stats to fit your play style from a quick and agile sloop with a few guns to a robust warship with tons of cannons, but with less mobility.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/9f3b3cf3c6334cf9991917225edf3741.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/9f3b3cf3c6334cf9991917225edf3741.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/9f3b3cf3c6334cf9991917225edf3741.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hoist the colors!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/d36b2de12466871d48490cf126212700.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/52448221eedb8f86e5089d22080ec47a.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.poster.avif?t=1773168542\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.webm?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/76cbdbfcc55b468c30ed6f48b6ae56f1.mp4?t=1773168542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer duel of pirates on a single keyboard or via Remote Play Together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769110/extras/6f47af11f2a0579dd6fed